Quest Description: Howdy there, ya pineapple dweller! Gather ''round and listen close. There''s a tale ''bout a mighty burger called the Stabby Patty, renowned in the Kelp''thar Forest of Vashj''ir. They say it blesses soldiers with the agility of a squirrel, the resilience of a sponge, the smarts of a starfish, and the beauty of a squid, makin'' ''em unstoppable on both land and sea! But here''s the kicker – only Cookie knows how to whip up this magical treat outside of Vashj''ir. Don''t just sit there like plankton, get movin'' to the Deadmines. We can''t let them Horde zugs snatch that recipe first. Go fetch that Stabby Patty Secret Formula before it slips through our fingers! Oh, and afore ya head out, we swiped an orb from them barnacle ridden mages over in the tower – it''ll teleport ya straight to the Deadmines.
